Definition: a partial excuse to mitigate censure
Example: an attempt to represent an offense as less serious than it appears by showing mitigating circumstances
Synonyms: verb, communication, extenuate, mitigation, mitigate, change, excuse, a, partial, to, censure, an, attempt, represent, offense, as, less, serious, than, it, appears, by, showing, mitigating, circumstances
Category: noun.communication
